<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Split Sheet Entry Updated</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #3498db;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .percentage-change {
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .percentage-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .old-percentage {
      color: #e74c3c;
      text-decoration: line-through;
    }
    .new-percentage {
      color: #27ae60;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .claim-button {
      background-color: #27ae60;
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #7f8c8d;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Split Sheet Entry Updated</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>
      
      <p>The split sheet for the song <strong>"{{songTitle}}"</strong> has been updated by the song owner, and your entry has changed.</p>
      
      <div class="percentage-change">
        <h3>Percentage Change:</h3>
        <div class="percentage-row">
          <span>Previous allocation: <span class="old-percentage">{{oldPercentage}}%</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="percentage-row">
          <span>New allocation: <span class="new-percentage">{{newPercentage}}%</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Important:</strong> Due to this update, you will need to claim your split again with the new percentage. Your previous claim has been invalidated to reflect the updated terms.</p>
      
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{claimLink}}" class="claim-button">Claim Your Updated Split</a>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>What you need to do:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Click the button above to review and claim your updated split</li>
        <li>Review the new percentage allocation</li>
        <li>Confirm your payout method is still current</li>
        <li>Complete the claim process to activate your updated split</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Your claim token is: <strong>{{claimToken}}</strong></p>
      
      <p>This link will take you to a page where you can review the updated split details and securely connect your payment information.</p>
      
      <p>If you have any questions about these changes or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ratedafrika.com">support@ratedafrika.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you,<br/>The ratedAfrika Team</p>
      <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:support@ratedafrika.com">support@ratedafrika.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 